data.description: From the moment you walk in you will love the grand entrance and tall ceilings. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bath.  On the first floor you will find a large family room, formal dining room with double windows and nice architecture. Home office facing the front yard, a half bath for guest, kitchen with siltstone counters, Island and tall cabinets.  The kitchen offers a breakfast room and breakfast bar and overlooks the family room.  Nice size laundry room with additional storage under the stairs. Primary bedroom with en-suite and a large walk-in closet.  The second story offers 3 nice size secondary bedrooms, with two bathrooms and a large game room. Residents enjoy scenic water views, walking trails, and neighborhood swimming pool. Nearby shopping!   All information is deemed correct but to be independently verified.
